transcript:
Executive: Hello
Customer: Hello
Executive: Haan ji bhai.
Customer: Haan ji sir.
Executive: Main Shubham bol raha tha pehle baat hai.
Customer: Main keh raha hu filhaal tum wo concern close kar do actually main bahar hu abhi kuch nahi hai time lagega tumhara open hai.
Executive: Toh main tumhe na shaam ko call karunga khud se 6 baje theek hai filhaal tum kar do please abhi.
Customer: Koi baat nahi ab close kar deta hu agar sir.
Executive: Tumse direct coordinate kar lunga phone utha lena filhaal.
Customer: Aap mujhe direct kar lena sir baki main connect already hu team se toh aap jo bhi connect karenge main aage kar dunga baki sir direct aa jayega sir.
Executive: Woh main kar dunga theek hai aap shaam shaam mein mujhe call kar lijiyega koi dikkat nahi theek hai.
Executive: Okay.
summary:

- Wants concern to be closed.

- Will need time as currently outside.



Resolution:

- Agreed to close the concern.

- Executive will call at 6 PM.
